lg-gram-manager (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Features:
    - Reader mode control
    - FN lock toggle
    - Fan mode selection (Silent/Optimal/Performance)
    - Battery charge limit (80%/100%)
    - USB charging when off
    - Keyboard backlight control
    - Touchpad LED control
  * Modern UI with light/dark theme support

